Program: Outlook
Title: 12/04/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00fvmx1
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 13 Apr 2011
Natalia Kaliada founded the Belarus Free Theatre with her husband and explains why they had to perform in secret before being forced into exile. Also, our reporter Mpho Lakaje discovers the strong bond that has developed between someone whose family has been affected by Aids and her mentor, even though they live thousands of miles apart. Show less